{"tid":2253790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本去年拒逾萬名外國人入境 中國人35%最多","createTime":"2020-10-22T11:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T12:16:09.000Z","uid":75656,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d0a7a39cadf03f1b7a0861ee4de0ebc564788259","tid":2253790,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T11:44:46.000Z","msg":"日本出入國居留管理廳統計，去年因謊報入境目的等原因而遭拒絕入境的外國人人數，達到1萬647人，相隔12年再度破萬人，其中最多的是中國人，約占35%。<br />\n<br />\n這些外國人被拒絕入境的理由，<span class=\"red\">大多是被懷疑要在日本非法工作，卻謊稱來觀光或探親</span>。因日本當局對其入境目的有所疑慮而拒絕入境的外國人高達8,890人，占83.5%。<br />\n<br />\n若從國家或地區來看，這1萬多名遭拒絕入境的外國人中，<span class=\"red\">中國人有3,765人最多，且比2018年大幅增加</span>。其次是泰國人1,398人，第三則是土耳其人925人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2082849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2082849&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=e447669a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2082849</a>"},{"pid":"ed1c2e7cdde3f0540f408895889c3c5c711285e2","tid":2253790,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T12:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}